{"tid":2491120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊:單純喊「結束一黨專政」口號 應該不會干犯顛覆國家政權罪","createTime":"2021-04-16T05:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:49:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"383c95638ac788f8f3dffb9f0c03d09abc9bb900","tid":2491120,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"本身是資深大律師的行政會議成員湯家驊表示，喊「結束一黨專政」口號會否違反國安法，視乎證據及意圖，不能一概而論，但呼籲大眾不要以身試法，「單純喊一喊口號，但無任何組織嘗試以武力或非法手段去推翻共產黨，應該不會干犯顛覆國家政權罪。但會不會因此干犯煽動罪，即煽惑其他人去組織、策劃，就要視乎實際情況，有無罪證去證明有人因此被他們煽動到，這個不能一概而論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/731000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F731000&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=cea51cdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F731000&h=ceec8a04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/731000</a>"},{"pid":"d04dd503139e296aed43bca0274b0a03808639e0","tid":2491120,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"有犯法就有犯法<br />\n冇犯法就冇犯法<br />\n講清楚啲啦低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a887c09db6855ba5a12fb3b8b0a216a71cc8ab5f","tid":2491120,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04dd503139e296aed43bca0274b0a03808639e0","tid":2491120,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"有犯法就有犯法<br />\n冇犯法就冇犯法<br />\n講清楚啲啦低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"佢呢排乜都係「應該」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faef66b574bdfe8d23b34c668aa5833b43